          <h1 class="mt-5">DINING is our specialization</h1>
          <p class="lead">The dinning experience at Savoey is one of its own kinds with its endless array of scrumptious cuisines from the worl d renowned cooking traditions. The experienced chefs at Savoey quench your appetite with their unrivaled cookery offering a blend of local and international delights on your table.</p>

          <p>Be it the local cuisines or family-style, continental, Italian or classical, Chinese or Thai, at Savoey you will get simply what is most satisfying for your taste buds and health.</p>

          <h2 class="mt-5">Café Aroma</h2>
          <p>One of the finest dinning opportunities in Lahore, Café Aroma brings to you all day dinning in an ambience which is perfect for eating and rejuvenating. It offers a vibrant setting and varied international cuisine experience in the best of environs. Under the direction and supervision of our renowned Executive Chef, you will get a chance to realize all the dreams of your taste buds in Café Aroma.</p>
