          <p>Valvet Lounge, the Heart of the House, is the most astounding restaurant at Savoey which is a feast for the appetite offering a wide array of mouthwatering delights and light serving to rejuvenate you. Providing you with the 12th floor city view, you get the most outstanding assortment including:</p>

          <ul>
            <li>Live BBQ, snacks
