          <h2 class="mt-5">In Room Dinning</h2>
          <p>The in-room dinning experience at Savoey is also full of delights for our valued guest. Those who wish to enjoy great flavors in the privacy of their own rooms can order from our extensive menu which is luscious as well as wholesome. You can order for in-room dining 24/7 at our room service who will look after the needs of your appetite with utmost courtesy.</p>

